@host = http://localhost:5190
@filePath = /absolute/path/to/sample.txt
@fileId = replace-with-file-id

### Upload a document
POST {{host}}/api/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=SmartDocuMindBoundary

--SmartDocuMindBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< {{filePath}}
--SmartDocuMindBoundary--

### Ask a question about the uploaded document
POST {{host}}/api/upload/ask-stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fileId": "{{fileId}}",
  "question": "Summarize this document.",
  "aiMode": "balanced"
}
